{"tid":145101,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(探討)點解D女人星期日唔肯訓，死都要同人傾電話","createTime":"2017-03-06T03:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T04:43:40.000Z","uid":71949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b37e15cf08e35ec5e299457cd0c3c19aab8407","tid":145101,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:52:00.000Z","msg":"我無論之前前度定現任女友都係，<br />\n星期日都唔肯訓，死都要同我傾電話，<br />\n搞到凌晨1,2點都唔肯訓，點勸佢訓都唔肯收線，我同佢星期一九點又要返工。<br />\n我差唔多7點要起身趕巴士，佢都係差唔多。<br />\n問佢地點解要咁<br />\n一係答你:咁我真係訓唔著嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係就:我唔想星期日咁快過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屌啦，星期五，星期六又唔見你地咁，<br />\n仲要星期日凌晨問你將來點規劃果類一諗起就煩既問題，Hea答又唔比，我屌啦。<br />\n<br />\n我同佢講:唔好咁痴線啦，個個星期日都係咁，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人地天日仲要返工架</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://holland.pk/hdke1ctz[/img一]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhdke1ctz%5B%2Fimg%E4%B8%80%5D&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=6e5139ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/hdke1ctz[/img一]</a>"},{"pid":"b56997f8c1c6daf04f653c3cdeeda584f4a2e465","tid":145101,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tcoek018\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftcoek018&h=bf092294&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b2ab1eceecb42dd0ced86ba0d84b8213f86d45b","tid":145101,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"次次結果佢都係超夜訓第日返工又話暈又話唔舒服，病，又要人地關心佢，又要陪睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b414a0a34a329a3d7ca8e09e1708e2c2f13c92ee","tid":145101,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"